Packages that use thothbot.squirrel.core.shared.core
thothbot.squirrel.core.client.renderers Here is located WebGL renderer. 
thothbot.squirrel.core.client.shader Here are all shaders and shader's related code. 
thothbot.squirrel.core.client.textures Here are textures which can be used by Materials. 
thothbot.squirrel.core.shared.cameras Different cameras which are used by renderer. 
thothbot.squirrel.core.shared.core Contains all core Objects such as Vectors, Matrices and so on which are used overall on the project. 
thothbot.squirrel.core.shared.curves Different Curves: 2D and 3D. 
thothbot.squirrel.core.shared.geometries Different Geometries which can be applied for the Geometry objects. 
thothbot.squirrel.core.shared.geometries.parametric Parametric Geometry which can be defined as a custom function. 
thothbot.squirrel.core.shared.helpers Here are some Geometric Objects which can be used as a helper for the Scene. 
thothbot.squirrel.core.shared.lights Here are all types of Light Objects used in the Scene. 
thothbot.squirrel.core.shared.materials Here are all Materials used for the Geometric Objects. 
thothbot.squirrel.core.shared.objects Here are all Geometric Objects used in the Scene. 
thothbot.squirrel.core.shared.scenes Here are Scene object - the main rendering object and all Scene additions such as fog. 
thothbot.squirrel.core.shared.utils Contains helper methods which are used overall in the project.
